room_title: Escape room "Wizards and Dragons" by Escape Now Houston in Houston
review: it was quite challenging, hard even, but we had a lot of fun! Jessica was our host and she was awesome!!! Will definitely do again!

room_title: Escape room "Wizards and Dragons" by Escape Now Houston in Houston
review: This was our first escape room & we had a blast!!!! The staff was really sweet too.  Loved the wizard & dragon room but would suggest doing it with more than 2 people.
